<h2 class="bold font-l">Aloy "the Anointed One"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When she was born, the Matriarchs couldn't agree on whether she was the daughter of All-Mother sent to save the Nora, or the spawn of the Metal Devil sent to awaken it, with Teersa believing the former and Lansra adamantly believing the latter. They were able to reach a compromise in making her an outcast, keeping her away from Nora society for their protection, in Lansra's mind, but keeping open the possibility for her to earn her place. As it turns out, she actually was born to save them and the rest of humanity (albeit without the religious implications). </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="890tsl" data-video-descrip="TWA brings up this trope in his video." data-video-title="Chosen Ones" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/890tsl_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/890tsl.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TheChosenOne" data-video-tropename="The Chosen One" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WebAnimation/TerribleWritingAdvice" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/890tsl.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Chosen Ones</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="m0pnzl" data-video-descrip="It was revealed that Clank was created by Orvus to watch over time and maintain the Great Clock." data-video-title="Clank" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/m0pnzl_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/m0pnzl.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TheChosenOne" data-video-tropename="The Chosen One" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/RatchetAndClankFutureACrackInTime" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/m0pnzl.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Clank</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="u2now8" data-video-descrip="Upon being revived, Neo displays the power to bend the Matrix to his will, confirming the fact that he is the One." data-video-title="&quot;He Is The One&quot;" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/u2now8_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/u2now8.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TheChosenOne" data-video-tropename="The Chosen One" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Film/TheMatrix,Franchise/Matrix" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/u2now8.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">"He Is The One"</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="hd8n5q" data-video-descrip="Scene from the 1992 film version of Buffy the Vampire Slayer. The movie opens on narration, explaining the role and plight of the Slayer as the most recent takes up the stake to hunt vampires." data-video-title="Buffy '92 [The Chosen One]" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/hd8n5q_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/hd8n5q.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/TheChosenOne" data-video-tropename="The Chosen One" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Film/BuffyTheVampireSlayer,Franchise/BuffyVerse" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/hd8n5q.jpg">
